# .git-blame-ignore-revs
#
# Commit hashes listed here are ignored by `git blame` when the user
# passes `--ignore-revs-file=.git-blame-ignore-revs` or configures
# `git config blame.ignoreRevsFile .git-blame-ignore-revs` locally.
#
# Phase 2 of the hygiene campaign will append the mass-reformat
# commit hash to this file in a single commit whose sole purpose is
# that reformat. Do not add unrelated commits here.
